{"tid":85460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［號外］人口增長與經濟發展","createTime":"2017-01-18T10:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T01:10:44.000Z","uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b60898ed6afe04f66eb503d0fa5849b80a09226","tid":85460,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:36:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Z3BYCK-3jPc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZ3BYCK-3jPc&d=cG8LQWL1ENegU4GLt3bP80sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=d10306c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Z3BYCK-3jPc</a><br />\n<br />\n入面提到一個research <br />\n指出人口增長率同經濟增長係唔太關係既<br />\n唔知道個research堅定流<br />\n但係佢提出一點就係唔好盲目追求人口持續增長<br />\n<br />\n巴絲們點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45935afadedf8886de2b6239c0ed306cf3487264","tid":85460,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:45:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68d45ec0189e21ebf59cc1f0de379bdeeea0ac7e","tid":85460,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:46:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c16818b678b9eacec8a084e8f852e560ee9fbf89","tid":85460,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:55:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05c989577b5ff59d0d5f43f0aec9b1aeb399db2f","tid":85460,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:57:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a03826603a8f73336e7aca26456955ecec7580f","tid":85460,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:58:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2f20d483e94bec3a1dbe275170addd9625cd5ba","tid":85460,"uid":42097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:58:43.000Z","msg":"好簡單<br />\n其實金錢呢樣野係無任何功能<br />\n只不過係當每個人都相信金錢係有價值既objective<br />\n先會令到呢樣野有value<br />\n真正有價值既野係水,食物,shelter ,etc<br />\n返正題，其實人越多，每人分到地球既資源就越少<br />\n經濟再點樣好都改變唔到呢個事實"},{"pid":"90c0f566dfe073aefdd6a7319c5afe49255